237
00:16:15,900 --> 00:16:18,000
Snow-- you don't have any.

238
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:20,400
It's 900 degrees out there.

239
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,400
Time-- you don't have any.

240
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:24,500
The Olympics
are in three months.

241
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:27,800
And me-- you don't have me.

242
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:31,300
As far as I'm concerned, the sport
of bobsledding no longer exists.

243
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:33,900
I don't want to do it,
I don't want to coach it...

244
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:37,100
and most of all--
and I mean most of all--

245
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:41,500
