Mr Blitzer...

265
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:08,300
but you can't walk away
from this:

266
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:11,200
20 years ago you came down here
to see if you could make...

267
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:13,500
a Jamaican sprinter
into a bobsledder...

268
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:16,000
and you never got that chance.

269
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,200
Look at me, Mr Blitzer.

270
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:20,200
I'm your chance.

271
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,400
Take it.

272
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:35,900
All right, everyone quiet down.

273
00:18:36,100 --> 00:18:38,000
Nice group here.

274
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:41,600
Now, for two of you lucky people,
our trip to the Olympics...

275
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,700
starts right now.

276
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:47,000
And I want to introduce you...

277
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:49,300
to Mr lrving Blitzer...

278
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:52,800
