get on with your real future. Right?

387
00:25:56,700 --> 00:25:59,400
- I know--
- Right?

388
00:25:59,700 --> 00:26:02,000
- Yes, sir.
- Good.

389
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:07,800
I'm going to tell your mother.

390
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:21,300
I guess we sure told him.

391
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:28,800
